WEBVTT

01:31.700 --> 01:35.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:35.980 --> 01:38.980
[Episode 20]

01:51.040 --> 01:52.050
This drought looks

01:52.920 --> 01:54.490
even worse than I expected.

01:55.200 --> 01:55.690
Right.

01:56.070 --> 01:57.130
The shops are all closed,

01:58.120 --> 02:00.420
and the townsfolk can barely get by.

02:01.120 --> 02:02.740
There's demonic energy from Han Ba everywhere.

02:04.870 --> 02:06.290
He really is clever,

02:07.430 --> 02:09.410
spreading his demonic energy all over the city.

02:10.150 --> 02:11.030
Now it's impossible to pin down

02:11.030 --> 02:12.260
his exact location.

02:14.190 --> 02:14.980
Bai Ze said

02:15.800 --> 02:17.290
that as soon as Han Ba spoke,

02:18.080 --> 02:19.850
the searing heat inside him would escape

02:20.310 --> 02:21.450
and bring drought upon the land.

02:22.750 --> 02:24.060
That's why he always kept his mouth shut

02:24.710 --> 02:25.450
and cultivated alone.

02:28.150 --> 02:29.730
Judging by the scale of this drought,

02:30.710 --> 02:31.570
Han Ba's probably

02:31.910 --> 02:33.720
turned into a chatterbox by now.

02:35.080 --> 02:35.540
By the way,

02:36.310 --> 02:37.540
did you tell You Chi

02:37.840 --> 02:39.060
about Ji Ling?

02:40.140 --> 02:40.680
Mother...

02:40.680 --> 02:41.500
Not yet.

02:41.500 --> 02:42.800
I'm hungry.

02:42.800 --> 02:43.690
I'm worried

02:43.750 --> 02:44.610
that if he finds out,

02:45.800 --> 02:47.170
every weasel in the streets

02:47.190 --> 02:48.060
will know too.

02:49.000 --> 02:50.660
That'll be no different from posting notices all over the city.

02:58.630 --> 02:58.980
See?

02:59.630 --> 03:00.540
We've only been apart for a while,

03:01.190 --> 03:02.540
and Wu Shiguang already misses me.

03:04.560 --> 03:06.400
Obviously, Wu Shiguang has ditched his friend

03:06.960 --> 03:07.950
now that he has a loved one.

03:08.790 --> 03:10.090
Why else did he dump you on me?

03:11.030 --> 03:11.970
Nonsense.

03:12.710 --> 03:14.080
I'm the unlucky one here,

03:15.240 --> 03:17.730
getting stuck with a scary brute like you

03:17.840 --> 03:18.950
to look for a place to stay.

03:21.030 --> 03:22.270
Look at this fierce face of yours.

03:23.710 --> 03:24.690
Even if we find an inn,

03:25.310 --> 03:26.540
they might not dare take us in.

03:28.590 --> 03:29.540
Have you heard of a saying?

03:29.750 --> 03:30.170
What saying?

03:32.080 --> 03:33.010
Weasel, meet your maker.

03:44.430 --> 03:45.540
There's not a soul in sight.

03:46.520 --> 03:47.990
How are we supposed to find a place to stay?

03:48.360 --> 03:49.130
Let's look around first.

03:55.590 --> 03:56.010
Here.

04:00.400 --> 04:00.850
What,

04:02.870 --> 04:03.500
you don't like it anymore?

04:06.560 --> 04:08.290
It doesn't really go with what I'm wearing today.

04:09.680 --> 04:10.780
And you think

04:11.800 --> 04:12.660
it goes well with me?

04:14.400 --> 04:15.660
Just hold it.

04:17.600 --> 04:18.290
Besides,

04:18.310 --> 04:20.020
I haven't seen Ji Ling in a very long time.

04:22.720 --> 04:24.490
Ji Ling...

04:25.190 --> 04:27.100
- All you ever talk about is Ji Ling. - Ji.

04:33.120 --> 04:34.020
Don't call me that

04:34.070 --> 04:35.050
in front of the others later.

04:35.520 --> 04:36.350
You don't like it?

04:36.870 --> 04:37.540
It's not that.

04:37.870 --> 04:39.580
It makes me sound like some half-grown kid.

04:39.680 --> 04:40.700
But it's cute.

04:44.000 --> 04:44.700
Fine.

04:45.390 --> 04:46.410
Call me whatever you like.

04:47.800 --> 04:49.410
Fair's fair.

04:49.950 --> 04:51.600
From now on, Ji, you can call me Wu too.

04:51.870 --> 04:52.590
Wu?

04:53.470 --> 04:54.530
Like the sound a fox makes?

04:55.230 --> 04:56.010
Awoo!

04:56.680 --> 04:58.580
Its name is Wu.

04:58.800 --> 04:59.250
Sorry,

04:59.560 --> 05:00.340
but the name's been taken.

05:01.510 --> 05:02.170
Master Dragon Deity,

05:02.950 --> 05:03.980
that kind of joke

05:04.070 --> 05:05.250
doesn't really suit you.

05:06.360 --> 05:07.050
Cut it out.

05:14.560 --> 05:15.660
Did Jiu Ying give you a hard time

05:16.120 --> 05:17.020
back in the Formless Moon?

05:19.720 --> 05:20.370
I'm fine.

05:21.480 --> 05:22.020
On the other hand,

05:22.820 --> 05:25.050
you used to be at each other's throats with Ji Ling,

05:25.310 --> 05:26.730
but now you two are getting along pretty well.

05:30.070 --> 05:31.170
A hundred years on the divine throne,

05:31.870 --> 05:32.810
walking on thin ice,

05:34.310 --> 05:35.580
pretending to be someone else,

05:37.000 --> 05:37.930
and living like a shadow,

05:39.240 --> 05:40.340
never able to speak the truth,

05:42.680 --> 05:43.540
he doesn't have it easy.

05:45.630 --> 05:46.730
He lived in loneliness for a century.

05:48.750 --> 05:50.280
But now that he's met Wuyi,

05:51.110 --> 05:52.690
he's got some youthful spirit back.

05:52.830 --> 05:53.880
Even the way he dresses

05:53.920 --> 05:55.170
has gotten younger.

05:55.630 --> 05:58.100
Wouldn't you call that an old tree coming back into bloom?

05:59.390 --> 06:00.580
You and Lu Wuyi

06:01.190 --> 06:02.370
are both thousand-year-old foxes.

06:03.040 --> 06:04.140
Compared to you two,

06:04.950 --> 06:05.900
Ji Ling and I

06:06.630 --> 06:07.460
are the tender shoots.

06:09.120 --> 06:11.420
You're siding with him already?

06:12.750 --> 06:15.020
People always say fox demons are heartless,

06:15.480 --> 06:18.610
but Wuyi takes love

06:19.270 --> 06:20.730
more seriously than anything.

06:21.240 --> 06:22.370
It's a blessing

06:22.510 --> 06:23.580
that he's won Wuyi's heart.

06:24.430 --> 06:26.730
Even if it comes with misfortune, he should accept it without complaint.

06:27.830 --> 06:28.540
Then what about you?

06:35.430 --> 06:36.340
You're a fox demon too.

06:40.160 --> 06:40.900
Where's your heart?

06:56.560 --> 06:57.810
Vacant rooms!

06:57.870 --> 06:59.250
Clean and comfortable rooms

06:59.270 --> 07:00.140
at fair prices!

07:00.310 --> 07:02.460
Don't miss out!

07:03.240 --> 07:04.290
A desert oasis

07:04.390 --> 07:05.540
and a spring in the wasteland,

07:05.720 --> 07:07.400
- this is the perfect haven for travelers! - With the whole city this desolate,

07:07.400 --> 07:08.930
someone's still drumming up business for an inn?

07:08.950 --> 07:09.930
It's definitely a trap.

07:24.070 --> 07:25.100
A trap?

07:26.390 --> 07:27.490
The inn is brightly lit

07:27.510 --> 07:28.370
and spotlessly clean.

07:28.480 --> 07:29.540
Don't go throwing that word around.

07:30.360 --> 07:31.580
Times are unusual right now,

07:31.600 --> 07:32.540
so we're running a special promotion.

07:32.920 --> 07:34.540
We're collecting curious stories from ordinary folk.

07:35.070 --> 07:36.410
If you two can offer us

07:36.430 --> 07:37.410
a good one,

07:38.000 --> 07:39.730
your stay is on the house.

07:40.190 --> 07:40.900
On the house?

07:43.120 --> 07:43.700
That sounds good.

07:44.310 --> 07:45.220
Where's your inn?

07:45.410 --> 07:45.850
Is it far?

07:45.850 --> 07:46.810
Not far at all.

07:47.430 --> 07:48.050
It's right here.

07:48.180 --> 07:50.420
[Chatter Inn]

07:51.070 --> 07:51.540
Wangyan!

07:51.800 --> 07:52.250
Wuyi.

07:52.560 --> 07:53.340
You're here too?

08:04.720 --> 08:05.580
What's going on?

08:07.560 --> 08:08.370
I scared him.

08:11.870 --> 08:12.980
Ji's all fair and pretty.

08:13.160 --> 08:14.220
How could he have scared anyone?

08:16.190 --> 08:17.170
Didn't we agree

08:17.190 --> 08:17.970
you wouldn't call me Ji?

08:18.000 --> 08:18.740
What's wrong,

08:18.920 --> 08:19.460
Ji?

08:20.070 --> 08:20.700
Ji?

08:23.430 --> 08:24.260
It seems

08:24.260 --> 08:25.440
the innkeeper

08:25.680 --> 08:26.540
knows Ji Ling.

08:29.190 --> 08:29.980
Of course he does.

08:30.480 --> 08:31.020
He

08:32.030 --> 08:33.250
is Han Ba.

08:37.960 --> 08:38.580
Is that so?

08:38.960 --> 08:39.420
Ji...

08:46.510 --> 08:47.220
I'm exhausted.

08:48.720 --> 08:49.420
I can't do this anymore.

08:50.480 --> 08:51.010
I can't.

08:51.910 --> 08:52.820
My legs are about to give out.

08:53.910 --> 08:55.010
You go find an inn.

08:55.960 --> 08:57.380
I'll just curl up in some hole by the road.

08:57.720 --> 08:58.180
No way.

08:59.360 --> 09:00.100
Then carry me.

09:07.720 --> 09:08.250
Listen.

09:09.120 --> 09:09.650
Walk on your own.

09:09.910 --> 09:10.490
I'm not carrying you.

09:10.750 --> 09:11.370
What?

09:12.030 --> 09:13.250
Listen. Don't turn around.

09:14.240 --> 09:15.060
There's a girl

09:15.480 --> 09:16.370
following me

09:16.840 --> 09:17.490
and sneaking looks at me.

09:19.970 --> 09:20.580
Hey!

09:20.960 --> 09:22.130
Get back here. What are you doing?

09:23.550 --> 09:24.530
She's following me.

09:25.510 --> 09:26.420
What nonsense.

09:26.670 --> 09:27.300
She's not blind.

09:28.120 --> 09:29.490
It's obvious which of us

09:30.030 --> 09:31.060
is more handsome.

09:33.480 --> 09:35.340
Miss, I'm You...

09:35.550 --> 09:37.220
Are you the one

09:37.240 --> 09:38.890
who used to be by Master Chi Wen's side?

09:41.720 --> 09:42.340
I'm Li Jie.

09:43.860 --> 09:45.730
Do... do you still remember me?

09:51.910 --> 09:53.250
Master Chi Wen,

09:53.910 --> 09:57.010
please... please watch over my great-grandmother.

09:57.510 --> 10:00.890
Please let her get better soon.

10:16.030 --> 10:17.820
Please... please let her

10:18.150 --> 10:20.370
recover quickly.

10:22.480 --> 10:23.420
Please.

10:28.270 --> 10:30.100
Master Chi Wen sent me to pass a message on to you.

10:31.510 --> 10:33.010
Your long vigil and prayers here

10:33.480 --> 10:35.130
show a devotion heaven and earth can witness.

10:35.630 --> 10:36.770
But birth, aging, sickness, and death

10:37.390 --> 10:38.820
are the ways of the world.

10:39.510 --> 10:40.700
Every mortal life

10:40.750 --> 10:41.850
has its end.

10:43.390 --> 10:44.420
The Dragon Deity's Power

10:45.240 --> 10:47.180
cannot be used to reverse the laws of nature.

10:50.240 --> 10:51.650
Instead of wasting your time

10:52.600 --> 10:53.730
kneeling here in prayer,

10:54.910 --> 10:56.250
you should spend more time with your family

10:57.120 --> 10:58.100
and cherish the days you have.

10:59.670 --> 11:01.370
Does the Master Dragon Deity know

11:02.440 --> 11:04.060
about all the suffering in this world?

11:07.910 --> 11:08.460
He does.

11:10.550 --> 11:11.940
Then does he just ignore it all?

11:14.910 --> 11:16.180
Master Dragon Deity said

11:18.440 --> 11:20.060
what carries us through suffering

11:20.720 --> 11:21.890
and helps us overcome evil

11:23.390 --> 11:24.700
is not the protection of the gods,

11:25.730 --> 11:26.880
but the hope and courage

11:27.840 --> 11:29.300
that never fade

11:30.550 --> 11:31.490
from our hearts.

11:38.530 --> 11:39.700
He asked me

11:39.840 --> 11:40.820
to return this to you.

11:49.320 --> 11:50.980
Do you remember this?

11:54.150 --> 11:54.610
I do.

11:58.360 --> 11:59.130
Master Dragon Deity,

12:00.000 --> 12:01.770
have you come to take back the Dragon Deity's Power?

12:04.030 --> 12:05.220
And you're telling me

12:05.910 --> 12:06.890
this man is a dragon,

12:09.000 --> 12:11.940
and these two are foxes over 1,000 years old?

12:12.960 --> 12:15.010
This is too much for me.

12:15.600 --> 12:16.650
I only wanted to run

12:16.670 --> 12:17.650
a small business

12:17.670 --> 12:18.500
and keep an inn.

12:18.750 --> 12:20.520
Why send

12:20.520 --> 12:21.940
such a force

12:22.080 --> 12:23.420
to come after me?

12:24.120 --> 12:25.220
Luo'an is parched with drought.

12:25.220 --> 12:26.010
Why do you think?

12:26.380 --> 12:27.610
Why did you run into the inn and hide?

12:28.870 --> 12:29.700
Did you think that door

12:29.720 --> 12:30.700
would keep me out?

12:31.380 --> 12:32.790
Why's the inn door busted?

12:33.030 --> 12:33.770
Did some bandit barge in

12:33.790 --> 12:35.460
and start looting and killing?

12:35.840 --> 12:36.270
Don't be scared.

12:36.480 --> 12:37.490
I'll take care of them!

12:41.150 --> 12:41.890
You're all here?

12:43.440 --> 12:44.650
You beat us again.

12:54.360 --> 12:55.220
My eyes

12:55.510 --> 12:56.340
are quite alluring.

13:05.200 --> 13:05.890
What are you all doing?

13:06.270 --> 13:07.220
Why is the mood so tense?

13:08.120 --> 13:08.650
Forcing...

13:12.360 --> 13:14.060
asking someone to hand over the Dragon Deity's Power.

13:16.600 --> 13:17.700
Are you afraid

13:17.910 --> 13:19.370
that once you hand it over,

13:19.750 --> 13:20.370
you'll die?

13:25.870 --> 13:27.060
These extra years I've lived,

13:27.080 --> 13:28.010
propped up by the Dragon Deity's Power,

13:28.440 --> 13:30.370
were stolen to begin with.

13:31.790 --> 13:32.580
I'm not afraid of dying.

13:34.550 --> 13:35.610
What I'm afraid of

13:38.080 --> 13:39.890
is that once I hand over the Dragon Deity's Power,

13:40.600 --> 13:41.890
the searing heat inside me

13:42.120 --> 13:43.300
will spiral out of control,

13:44.440 --> 13:45.460
and drought will break out

13:48.240 --> 13:49.250
across the whole world.

13:51.030 --> 13:52.490
Once we gather all of the Dragon Deity's Power,

13:54.390 --> 13:55.610
he can become a true dragon,

13:56.120 --> 13:56.850
summon wind and rain,

13:57.720 --> 13:58.580
and end the drought.

14:00.510 --> 14:01.300
Helping him become a dragon

14:02.080 --> 14:03.420
was also Master Chi Wen's wish.

14:04.510 --> 14:05.460
Master Chi Wen?

14:05.840 --> 14:06.730
Is everyone

14:06.750 --> 14:08.530
talking about themselves in the third person now?

14:10.630 --> 14:11.820
So you're the Tenth Dragon Son

14:11.820 --> 14:13.130
we've all been waiting for?

14:14.270 --> 14:14.820
That's right.

14:17.870 --> 14:18.250
What is it?

14:19.270 --> 14:19.850
Don't I look the part?

14:19.880 --> 14:20.750
I wouldn't dare say that.

14:22.010 --> 14:23.180
I just didn't expect

14:23.440 --> 14:25.520
the Tenth Dragon Son to look so utterly ordinary.

14:25.750 --> 14:26.770
You've hidden it well.

14:28.790 --> 14:29.180
See?

14:29.440 --> 14:30.370
I told you.

14:31.200 --> 14:32.530
You should've bought some nicer outfits.

14:33.390 --> 14:34.340
Look at Ji Ling.

14:34.610 --> 14:35.820
He dresses so flamboyantly every day.

14:36.600 --> 14:37.420
I heard that.

14:38.080 --> 14:39.700
Both of my ears heard every word.

14:43.870 --> 14:44.530
These past years,

14:46.080 --> 14:47.580
my injuries have only worsened.

14:48.910 --> 14:50.340
The only thing that can suppress

14:51.030 --> 14:52.490
the searing heat inside me is the Dragon Deity's Power.

14:53.670 --> 14:54.580
I didn't take back my power

14:55.120 --> 14:56.010
to break the oath,

14:56.870 --> 14:58.100
but to suppress the searing heat.

15:00.960 --> 15:01.980
Are your injuries

15:03.390 --> 15:04.610
really incurable?

15:09.840 --> 15:10.370
That's why

15:11.910 --> 15:12.940
this drought befell Luo'an.

15:14.520 --> 15:15.730
I see.

15:16.390 --> 15:17.730
But Luo'an was doomed to drought.

15:18.320 --> 15:19.950
Even if you had kept your mouth shut,

15:20.150 --> 15:21.760
it wouldn't have changed anything.

15:23.630 --> 15:24.820
I only started talking

15:26.360 --> 15:28.340
to fulfill a young girl's wish.

15:34.260 --> 15:39.380
♪The wind blows by, and memories sway with dreams♪

15:40.300 --> 15:45.300
♪I stay silent, afraid the fire in my heart will rise♪

15:46.860 --> 15:50.060
♪Reed flowers sway with burning heat♪

15:50.300 --> 15:53.500
♪Shaking the story into something blurred and worn♪

15:53.740 --> 15:55.740
♪I am only♪

15:55.860 --> 15:58.900
♪A murmuring traveler through wind and snow♪

16:01.100 --> 16:06.380
♪Watching the evening glow turn cold and fade into night♪

16:07.740 --> 16:12.780
♪Watching every stroke and mark spell out reluctance♪

16:14.340 --> 16:17.500
♪Watching spider lilies bloom across the hills♪

16:17.660 --> 16:20.980
♪Watching the one in my dreams send back bitterness...♪

16:21.720 --> 16:22.890
She's the girl I was talking about.

16:24.320 --> 16:25.130
Her name is Mu Long.

16:27.390 --> 16:28.330
These are all stories

16:28.330 --> 16:30.300
she and I collected by waiving lodging fees.

16:31.440 --> 16:33.620
I want to help Mu Long finish her story collection.

16:34.120 --> 16:36.010
All that's missing now is an ending.

16:38.320 --> 16:39.340
I've watched

16:39.390 --> 16:40.580
Mu Long grow up.

16:41.200 --> 16:42.250
Since childhood, she's had a stutter,

16:42.750 --> 16:43.370
kept to herself,

16:43.600 --> 16:44.770
and struggled to get along with people.

16:45.600 --> 16:47.220
The only thing that can make her speak

16:47.720 --> 16:49.300
is when it concerns this collection of stories.

16:51.150 --> 16:52.610
I have to help her finish it.

16:55.960 --> 16:56.820
Masters and madams,

16:57.240 --> 16:58.100
please give me one more day.

16:58.720 --> 16:59.580
Just one more day.

17:00.750 --> 17:01.220
Tomorrow,

17:02.320 --> 17:03.980
I will return the Dragon Deity's Power.

17:14.400 --> 17:14.900
Do you...

17:15.440 --> 17:17.420
do you really have good stories?

17:25.880 --> 17:26.290
All right!

17:27.160 --> 17:28.290
Based on how good

17:28.310 --> 17:29.810
your stories were,

17:30.070 --> 17:31.420
I've assigned your rooms.

17:32.070 --> 17:33.810
From the most luxurious to the most modest,

17:33.960 --> 17:36.420
they're divided into Heaven, Earth,

17:36.680 --> 17:37.290
and Human tiers.

17:37.990 --> 17:38.680
Sleep well,

17:39.450 --> 17:40.010
everyone.

17:54.400 --> 17:54.940
Han Ba,

17:55.550 --> 17:57.420
how dare you put Master Dragon Deity in a Human-tier room?

18:11.160 --> 18:11.770
An Earth-tier room?

18:12.550 --> 18:13.010
Got a problem?

18:20.400 --> 18:21.140
We need two rooms.

18:45.310 --> 18:46.570
As I recall,

18:47.200 --> 18:49.140
this lady didn't tell a story just now.

18:49.720 --> 18:51.180
Are you planning to sleep on the street tonight?

18:52.960 --> 18:54.140
I only tell my stories

18:54.270 --> 18:55.530
to the one I love.

18:57.640 --> 18:58.050
Go on.

18:58.750 --> 19:00.250
I don't mind being the one you love.

19:02.240 --> 19:03.310
But I do.

19:04.050 --> 19:05.460
I already have someone I love.

19:06.270 --> 19:07.460
He is the one I love,

19:08.550 --> 19:09.570
and that's settled for life.

19:11.310 --> 19:12.770
I already have someone I love.

19:13.240 --> 19:15.140
He is the one I love,

19:15.550 --> 19:16.670
and that's settled for life.

19:21.960 --> 19:23.250
Then the most comfortable Heaven-tier suite

19:24.160 --> 19:24.700
belongs to you.

19:28.310 --> 19:28.980
Thank you, sir.

19:38.750 --> 19:39.250
Here.

19:41.070 --> 19:42.620
I don't accept charity.

19:45.070 --> 19:45.980
Drop the act.

19:47.110 --> 19:48.460
Could you save a little face for me?

20:16.820 --> 20:17.530
What are you doing?

20:18.960 --> 20:20.380
Someone's unhappy.

20:20.380 --> 20:21.700
I need to cheer him up.

20:23.830 --> 20:24.180
I'm good.

20:28.240 --> 20:29.600
Why are you being petty?

20:30.080 --> 20:31.620
I am broad-minded.

20:32.590 --> 20:34.330
I just think this wine tastes

20:36.920 --> 20:37.460
very sour.

20:39.920 --> 20:40.490
Sour?

20:44.400 --> 20:45.460
How is it sour?

20:45.640 --> 20:46.330
You're way sourer.

20:48.310 --> 20:48.770
Well?

20:49.550 --> 20:50.010
Is it sweet?

20:51.720 --> 20:52.250
It is.

20:55.550 --> 20:56.420
I think it's sweet too.

20:59.880 --> 21:00.810
A Heaven-tier room.

21:05.240 --> 21:08.220
Yunjin brocade, silk bedding, and incense.

21:09.840 --> 21:10.870
Who would've thought

21:11.830 --> 21:13.620
that gaudy, flashy stuff like this

21:14.550 --> 21:16.090
would be enough to make you so happy?

21:19.920 --> 21:21.860
Back at the Shilin Sect,

21:22.240 --> 21:22.980
someone prepared

21:23.000 --> 21:24.490
all this for me too.

21:24.610 --> 21:25.520
Who was it?

21:30.350 --> 21:32.410
And I remember someone saying...

21:32.710 --> 21:34.330
I don't accept charity.

21:34.920 --> 21:37.180
Don't think you can wear down my resolve

21:38.400 --> 21:40.220
with fine clothes and good food.

21:41.750 --> 21:42.380
Who was that?

21:44.270 --> 21:45.290
Why do you know everything?

21:46.880 --> 21:48.010
Does everyone in the Shilin Sect

21:48.070 --> 21:49.640
have special sight and hearing?

21:50.790 --> 21:51.590
Take a guess.

21:53.680 --> 21:54.250
Take a guess?

21:58.030 --> 21:58.460
You tell me.

22:00.350 --> 22:01.390
Are you going to tell me or not?

22:03.170 --> 22:04.150
It won't tell me.

22:05.640 --> 22:06.810
Then don't force it.

22:07.650 --> 22:08.420
Then you tell me.

22:09.030 --> 22:09.900
Then go on and ask it.

22:09.960 --> 22:10.700
I don't remember either.

22:12.460 --> 22:13.130
Tell me!

22:14.120 --> 22:15.170
Yes, you.

22:15.250 --> 22:15.910
Say it!

22:35.220 --> 22:40.060
♪A silent parting spreads like a sea of fog♪

22:41.260 --> 22:45.100
♪How do you say goodbye without regret?♪

22:47.060 --> 22:52.460
♪If even longing for an ordinary life is folly♪

22:53.060 --> 22:57.260
♪Who is still whispering, stranded in the river of time?♪

22:58.380 --> 23:04.500
♪Watch the spring breeze stir the warm sun, flowers across the hills♪

23:04.860 --> 23:10.660
♪Summer days run long, and flowing rain carries me afar♪

23:11.300 --> 23:16.820
♪Autumn turns cool, and fallen leaves become the clothes of dreams♪

23:17.260 --> 23:23.300
♪A face worn old by wind, snow, and frost♪

23:24.340 --> 23:29.100
♪The opening of the story is but a blank line♪

23:30.540 --> 23:34.660
♪The ending in disarray, like youth drawing to a close♪

23:39.340 --> 23:41.380
♪Eyes brim with tears♪

23:45.260 --> 23:46.580
♪Don't forget♪

23:56.750 --> 23:58.120
May I have a look?

23:59.200 --> 23:59.860
No.

23:59.860 --> 24:02.260
Not even Mr. Yan has read any of these.

24:02.830 --> 24:04.860
No one gets to read my stories

24:04.920 --> 24:05.980
until I've finished all of them.

24:09.500 --> 24:11.490
Why do you like writing stories?

24:12.650 --> 24:14.100
My great-grandmother

24:14.100 --> 24:16.310
used to tell me stories all the time.

24:17.640 --> 24:17.980
She...

24:18.240 --> 24:19.090
she always said

24:19.270 --> 24:20.220
that since I stuttered,

24:20.510 --> 24:23.660
writing stories suited me better.

24:25.480 --> 24:26.700
Too bad

24:27.440 --> 24:27.860
she...

24:28.270 --> 24:29.530
she'll never get to read them.

24:33.400 --> 24:34.490
Everything in this world

24:34.880 --> 24:35.810
fades away eventually.

24:36.510 --> 24:37.620
But there's a saying:

24:38.790 --> 24:41.220
"Writers never truly die."

24:42.270 --> 24:43.530
As long as their stories are read,

24:44.030 --> 24:45.100
the days

24:45.110 --> 24:47.090
they wrote down can be relived again.

24:48.640 --> 24:50.380
Your great-grandmother must be in your stories, right?

24:51.440 --> 24:52.460
Then she will always

24:52.480 --> 24:53.860
exist in this world.

24:55.880 --> 24:57.810
She said that too.

24:58.480 --> 24:59.490
Stories

25:00.240 --> 25:01.980
can weave the wishes

25:02.480 --> 25:04.770
people dare not speak of

25:05.510 --> 25:07.700
and their regrets

25:08.750 --> 25:11.380
into dreams of fiction.

25:11.880 --> 25:12.940
The people in stories

25:13.920 --> 25:15.330
never die.

25:16.110 --> 25:17.420
I wonder whether my regret

25:19.240 --> 25:20.770
will ever have a happy ending.

25:24.920 --> 25:25.290
Here, Miss Mu.

25:26.550 --> 25:27.700
Th... thank you.

25:31.680 --> 25:33.330
Your regret?

25:34.200 --> 25:35.490
Do... do you mean

25:36.070 --> 25:37.620
the girl in your story today,

25:38.640 --> 25:40.710
the one who made you a bracelet?

25:46.790 --> 25:47.450
Yes.

25:48.440 --> 25:49.290
It's a pity.

25:50.750 --> 25:51.700
My bracelet broke.

25:53.400 --> 25:54.050
I'm waiting for her.

25:55.240 --> 25:56.290
And I hope that one day,

25:57.110 --> 25:58.180
she'll be willing

25:58.510 --> 25:59.490
to make me another bracelet.

26:02.000 --> 26:02.900
No... no,

26:03.480 --> 26:04.420
that's not right.

26:05.590 --> 26:06.050
Why not?

26:09.070 --> 26:10.500
Because this is

26:10.520 --> 26:11.970
your story.

26:12.320 --> 26:13.500
You... you can't just wait.

26:13.680 --> 26:15.130
You need to write it yourself

26:15.910 --> 26:17.570
to get the ending you want.

26:18.510 --> 26:18.970
You...

26:19.400 --> 26:21.970
you can make a bracelet yourself.

27:24.350 --> 27:25.250
Ji Ling, you've really

27:26.270 --> 27:27.290
got a petty streak.

27:28.270 --> 27:29.420
I shared good food and wine with you,

27:30.030 --> 27:30.980
and you're still ignoring me.

28:20.920 --> 28:21.770
Big drumstick.

28:21.880 --> 28:22.700
Big drumstick.

28:22.920 --> 28:23.940
Big drumstick.

28:25.960 --> 28:26.620
Miss Mu?

28:28.880 --> 28:29.740
She's asleep.

28:35.510 --> 28:36.180
Let me take a look.

28:42.960 --> 28:45.490
"The Great Demon and Little Pomegranate."

28:45.510 --> 28:46.220
What kind of writing is this?

28:46.220 --> 28:47.160
[The Great Demon and Little Pomegranate]

28:47.160 --> 28:47.860
It's so ugly.

28:52.240 --> 28:52.900
Miss Mu Long...

28:53.030 --> 28:54.150
What are you doing?

28:54.680 --> 28:55.160
You...

28:55.200 --> 28:57.620
- you've stained my manuscript! - I'm sorry.

28:57.960 --> 28:59.140
I forgot my hands were covered in grease.

28:59.480 --> 29:00.250
Don't worry...

29:01.420 --> 29:02.990
Hey, don't cry.

29:03.510 --> 29:04.090
I know.

29:04.110 --> 29:04.860
I'll go find Wangyan.

29:05.160 --> 29:06.010
She knows magic.

29:06.480 --> 29:07.380
I'll go get her right now.

29:07.960 --> 29:08.570
Wangyan!

29:09.160 --> 29:10.140
Help, Wangyan!

29:10.440 --> 29:11.940
Wangyan, where are you?

29:12.790 --> 29:14.420
Wangyan, help!

29:14.420 --> 29:15.250
Wangyan!

29:15.660 --> 29:16.620
Wangyan!

29:18.420 --> 29:19.250
Wangyan!

29:23.030 --> 29:23.940
Wangyan!

29:39.000 --> 29:39.490
Wangyan...

30:00.960 --> 30:01.570
Ji Ling,

30:02.480 --> 30:03.860
why did you do this?

30:09.400 --> 30:10.770
You can go kill Chi Wen now.

30:34.680 --> 30:36.010
Wu Shiguang is under Jiu Ying's control.

30:38.170 --> 30:40.130
You really did keep your promise.

30:41.240 --> 30:42.520
Now you can sit

30:44.030 --> 30:46.000
on the Dragon Deity's throne

30:46.960 --> 30:47.940
forever.

30:53.830 --> 30:55.460
You killed my sister.

30:57.510 --> 30:59.090
I'll never forgive you.

31:16.240 --> 31:16.900
It was a dream.

31:28.030 --> 31:28.570
Mu Long.

31:39.960 --> 31:40.420
How?

31:53.750 --> 31:55.090
Not even the Dragon Deity's Power could...

31:55.510 --> 31:56.940
This person doesn't seem to fear magic.

32:09.640 --> 32:10.380
Who was that?

32:10.880 --> 32:11.700
Why did they know

32:11.720 --> 32:12.490
my bladework so well?

32:12.680 --> 32:13.490
They didn't know it,

32:14.270 --> 32:14.980
but they could predict

32:15.000 --> 32:15.900
every strike you made.

32:16.510 --> 32:17.620
What in the world is going on?

32:19.480 --> 32:20.290
There's only

32:21.750 --> 32:22.420
one person I know

32:24.510 --> 32:25.420
who's capable of that.

32:29.880 --> 32:30.860
Where are Ji Ling and Lu Wuyi?

32:34.400 --> 32:35.010
Master Dragon Deity.

32:36.750 --> 32:37.380
Master Dragon Deity?

32:53.070 --> 32:53.660
Wuyi.

32:54.680 --> 32:55.330
Wuyi?

33:00.350 --> 33:01.490
Master Dragon Deity isn't in his room.

33:03.590 --> 33:04.660
Is Lu Wuyi gone too?

33:13.590 --> 33:14.010
Li Jie,

33:14.960 --> 33:15.810
what are you doing?

33:27.600 --> 33:28.930
Were you two

33:29.590 --> 33:31.030
in the room the whole time?

33:31.830 --> 33:32.570
Wangyan...

34:01.790 --> 34:02.330
Wu,

34:04.000 --> 34:05.380
what in the world is going on?

34:08.190 --> 34:09.130
What are you trying to do?

34:19.590 --> 34:20.050
Mu Long?

34:22.230 --> 34:22.690
Mu Long?

34:30.880 --> 34:32.690
If Mu Long can't go back to normal,

34:34.920 --> 34:35.820
none of you are getting

34:35.840 --> 34:37.090
the Dragon Deity's Power.

34:37.760 --> 34:38.820
Are you threatening us?

34:40.030 --> 34:40.740
I know.

34:41.760 --> 34:42.690
There's no way I can beat

34:43.440 --> 34:44.860
two foxes from the Formless Moon

34:44.920 --> 34:45.740
and two dragons.

34:46.760 --> 34:47.820
But I've already

34:48.150 --> 34:49.420
hidden away the Dragon Deity's Power.

34:50.360 --> 34:51.740
If you don't save Mu Long...

34:52.280 --> 34:52.860
We will.

34:56.920 --> 34:57.820
I can try.

34:59.320 --> 35:00.860
She's under Word Magic.

35:11.920 --> 35:12.530
Master Dragon Deity,

35:13.190 --> 35:14.610
a person in black attacked Mu Long just now.

35:20.150 --> 35:21.490
Go investigate with Wu Shiguang

35:22.150 --> 35:22.820
and the others.

35:24.360 --> 35:24.900
What about you?

35:25.960 --> 35:26.940
Don't you need me with you?

35:28.530 --> 35:30.380
I have something more important to do.

35:33.800 --> 35:34.340
Understood.

35:56.110 --> 35:58.170
I can't wake her.

36:01.510 --> 36:02.440
Whoever cast the spell

36:02.710 --> 36:04.060
is stronger than I am.

36:04.590 --> 36:06.410
But Word Magic is the Formless Moon's specialty.

36:06.670 --> 36:07.610
Besides someone from the Formless Moon,

36:07.960 --> 36:09.010
who would know this spell?

36:11.960 --> 36:12.490
Xiaowei.

36:13.440 --> 36:14.210
Xiaowei?

36:16.030 --> 36:16.980
You mean Ji Ling?

36:17.840 --> 36:19.210
How dare you suspect Master Dragon Deity?

36:22.960 --> 36:23.650
He can use

36:23.670 --> 36:25.130
Xiaowei's spells through his Spirit-Binding Ring.

36:25.480 --> 36:26.530
Of course I suspect him.

36:27.230 --> 36:28.420
But didn't you just say

36:29.670 --> 36:31.130
Ji Ling was with your sister?

36:32.550 --> 36:33.570
Maybe Wuyi

36:33.920 --> 36:35.130
was helping Ji Ling cover it up.

36:36.280 --> 36:37.860
With all that fighting in the front courtyard,

36:38.550 --> 36:39.650
how could the Dragon Deity

36:40.000 --> 36:41.260
not have heard anything?

36:43.400 --> 36:43.860
Wangyan,

36:44.550 --> 36:46.210
why do you suspect Ji Ling so much?

36:47.400 --> 36:48.420
Do you know something?

36:55.830 --> 36:56.560
No.

36:57.960 --> 36:58.680
I just think

36:58.680 --> 37:00.450
the person in black was too strong.

37:00.670 --> 37:02.090
Even together, we couldn't beat them.

37:03.360 --> 37:03.900
Commander Li,

37:04.550 --> 37:05.490
aside from Ji Ling,

37:05.880 --> 37:07.820
who else knows your bladework that well?

37:18.800 --> 37:20.420
Why don't you suspect Lu Wuyi?

37:24.190 --> 37:24.690
You said

37:25.280 --> 37:26.420
she was covering up for Ji Ling.

37:27.230 --> 37:28.900
Why couldn't it be Ji Ling covering for her instead?

37:32.230 --> 37:33.010
You also said to me...

37:33.360 --> 37:34.170
There's only

37:34.840 --> 37:35.690
one person I know

37:37.590 --> 37:38.780
who's capable of that.

37:40.030 --> 37:41.210
Were you referring

37:42.880 --> 37:44.090
to Lu Wuyi?

37:46.960 --> 37:47.460
Listen.

37:48.320 --> 37:49.530
Is it possible

37:50.670 --> 37:52.610
that both of you are wrong?

37:53.550 --> 37:54.780
What if the two of them were working together

37:55.880 --> 37:57.300
and covering for each other?

38:00.800 --> 38:01.770
What secret is hidden

38:01.770 --> 38:02.720
in the first chapter of this manuscript?

38:03.840 --> 38:05.650
Why would the person in black go to such lengths over it?

38:09.190 --> 38:10.090
I haven't read it either.

38:11.320 --> 38:12.650
Mu Long said no one was allowed to read it

38:13.030 --> 38:13.980
until it was finished.

38:16.590 --> 38:18.340
Maybe it has something to do with my memories.

38:21.920 --> 38:23.090
Do you know me?

38:30.360 --> 38:31.860
So you're finally willing to talk about this.

38:33.070 --> 38:34.650
I thought you were pretending not to know me

38:35.670 --> 38:37.010
because there was something you couldn't say.

38:38.070 --> 38:39.460
I even played along with you.

38:43.630 --> 38:44.690
You really don't remember?

38:47.030 --> 38:48.050
Jiu Ying tampered

38:48.070 --> 38:48.820
with my memories.

38:49.480 --> 38:50.420
Any memories I had of you

38:51.280 --> 38:52.090
are gone.

38:54.400 --> 38:55.820
Little Pomegranate...

38:57.360 --> 38:58.300
Little Pomegranate...

38:59.480 --> 39:00.610
Little Pomegranate?

39:01.030 --> 39:01.940
What did Miss Mu say?

39:04.230 --> 39:05.300
Little Pomegranate?

39:07.760 --> 39:08.780
- What was it again? - What,

39:09.710 --> 39:10.420
itching for a beating again?

39:11.550 --> 39:12.650
Want me to scratch you with my blade?

39:12.760 --> 39:13.530
Be quiet.

39:14.400 --> 39:15.380
I'm almost remembering it.

39:17.920 --> 39:19.130
Let me show you a place.

39:20.000 --> 39:20.690
Maybe

39:21.360 --> 39:22.300
it will clear things up.

39:24.400 --> 39:25.090
And maybe

39:26.320 --> 39:27.570
it'll help you remember something too.

39:51.150 --> 39:52.280
Thank you.

39:58.630 --> 40:00.090
Sister, higher.

40:00.960 --> 40:02.570
Sister, higher!

40:10.440 --> 40:10.860
What is it?

40:13.920 --> 40:14.490
Nothing.

40:35.630 --> 40:37.380
This used to be Mu Long's great-grandmother's home,

40:38.400 --> 40:39.940
where she lived as a child.

40:42.960 --> 40:43.690
Where she lived?

40:48.630 --> 40:49.380
I remember now!

40:49.480 --> 40:50.260
You scared me.

40:50.480 --> 40:51.020
The manuscript!

40:51.230 --> 40:52.420
The first chapter of that manuscript

40:52.960 --> 40:54.210
was Little Pomegranate's story.

40:55.030 --> 40:55.860
The moment I heard

40:55.880 --> 40:56.900
the words "Little Pomegranate,"

40:57.590 --> 40:58.130
I felt like I'd

40:59.230 --> 41:00.010
seen them somewhere before.

41:01.110 --> 41:03.570
"The Great Demon and Little Pomegranate."

41:03.690 --> 41:04.770
[The Great Demon and Little Pomegranate]
What kind of writing is this?

41:05.110 --> 41:05.740
It's so ugly.

41:06.510 --> 41:07.260
The handwriting

41:07.630 --> 41:09.010
was all crooked.

41:09.190 --> 41:09.690
It was ugly.

41:11.400 --> 41:11.940
Really ugly.

41:13.590 --> 41:14.260
But still, I recognized

41:14.280 --> 41:15.480
the words "Little" and "Pomegranate."

41:16.030 --> 41:16.690
But

41:17.710 --> 41:18.900
Mu Long's handwriting is very neat.

41:19.440 --> 41:20.490
How could it be crooked?

41:21.480 --> 41:22.380
She had too much to drink.

41:23.110 --> 41:23.820
Shut it.

41:48.030 --> 41:49.650
Little Pomegranate.

41:56.630 --> 41:57.610
Little Pomegranate?

41:58.000 --> 41:58.760
Why does Little Pomegranate

41:58.760 --> 42:00.070
look like she's crying?

42:04.360 --> 42:05.490
Isn't that Wangyan?

42:15.630 --> 42:16.190
This...

42:17.320 --> 42:18.220
this really is me.

42:20.400 --> 42:22.140
But why would I be in this painting?

42:23.590 --> 42:25.340
And that tall, handsome fellow in the back

42:26.630 --> 42:27.380
is Mr. Yan.

42:28.630 --> 42:29.210
The painter is

42:29.670 --> 42:30.300
Cui Jun.

42:32.670 --> 42:33.570
Who's Cui Jun?

42:35.510 --> 42:36.210
Maybe

42:37.710 --> 42:38.570
I can try something.

43:03.320 --> 43:04.370
Where did Wu Shiguang and Wangyan go?

43:04.630 --> 43:05.900
How did they disappear in the blink of an eye?

43:07.400 --> 43:08.610
They've gone into the painting.

43:09.320 --> 43:10.420
Why did they leave me behind?

43:11.400 --> 43:12.260
What good would you do?

43:12.590 --> 43:13.300
What good would I do?

43:14.030 --> 43:14.900
I figured it out already.

43:16.150 --> 43:17.140
The girl in the painting

43:17.230 --> 43:17.980
is Little Pomegranate.

43:18.440 --> 43:19.360
And this story

43:19.440 --> 43:20.810
must have something to do with Mr. Yan.

43:21.280 --> 43:22.260
As for the great demon,

43:23.070 --> 43:23.610
that's you,

43:24.510 --> 43:25.130
Han Ba!

43:26.280 --> 43:26.650
Am I right?

43:28.840 --> 43:29.460
Pretty sharp, aren't I?

43:31.670 --> 43:32.460
Good for you.

43:33.590 --> 43:35.050
You've figured out what everyone already knows.

43:38.880 --> 43:40.210
Your story with Little Pomegranate

43:40.400 --> 43:41.300
must've been full of longing

43:41.320 --> 43:41.940
and heartbreak.

43:42.550 --> 43:43.420
Come on, tell us already.

43:49.840 --> 43:50.490
My name is Su Jian.

43:50.840 --> 43:52.090
What's your name?

43:54.000 --> 43:55.210
Why won't you say anything?

43:55.280 --> 43:57.380
You won't even tell me your name?

44:12.780 --> 44:13.940
♪It's your light♪

44:14.140 --> 44:16.020
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

44:16.180 --> 44:19.300
♪That set the night alight♪

44:19.660 --> 44:26.180
♪And lead me through the fight♪

44:27.940 --> 44:29.820
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

44:30.260 --> 44:34.700
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

44:35.500 --> 44:37.180
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

44:37.340 --> 44:42.740
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

44:43.500 --> 44:48.900
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

44:51.220 --> 44:57.260
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

44:58.220 --> 45:00.380
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

45:00.660 --> 45:05.500
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

45:05.860 --> 45:08.180
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

45:08.380 --> 45:13.460
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

45:13.700 --> 45:15.700
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

45:15.980 --> 45:20.340
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

45:21.340 --> 45:28.300
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

45:44.860 --> 45:47.820
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

45:48.900 --> 45:52.300
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

45:53.100 --> 45:55.620
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

45:55.860 --> 45:58.940
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

45:59.340 --> 46:01.660
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

46:02.180 --> 46:06.580
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

46:06.820 --> 46:08.980
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

46:09.380 --> 46:14.340
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

46:14.580 --> 46:15.740
♪It's your light♪

46:15.940 --> 46:17.780
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

46:17.980 --> 46:21.100
♪That set the night alight♪

46:21.860 --> 46:31.300
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
